name: NPC Joe is just a simple farmer ( CREEPERShateCATS , Level 1 , Season 1 )
description: NPC Joe is farming . Wheat fields glow in the sun . Creepers lurking in the background . A black cat in the background . NPC Joe is just a simple farmer in a world full of sociopathic creepers. So yeah. Let Joe farm and have a nice day, weirdos.
